title: Looking for JUNGLER Main GOLD+ (5s Ranked Team)
body:
My team and I are looking for a Jungler who is Gold+, is active and can play a few different champs. Very easy going team, non flamers preffered. Contact me via this or in game.

IGN: VaniShz
Skype: jaison.sfak

Thanks guys

replies.body:
Hey, Jungle main here, I jungle at a Plat level, was Plat 2 in season 4, had a bad placement series and am now silver 1
But don't let my current solo queue make the choice for you :)
If you still need a jungler I'm available was S4 haven't finished promos yet, but can get to Gold if needed but its up to you. You could always give me a trial run if you need asap.
